<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Mini-CRM + Landing Page Tracking </title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <%= csp_meta_tag %>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'LOH', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
    <%= javascript_pack_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
  </head>

  <body>

    <header class="d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-center py-3 mb-4 border-bottom" id="navigation-header">
        <a href="/" class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3 mb-md-0 me-md-auto text-dark text-decoration-none">
            <span class="fs-4">Mini CRM</span>
        </a>

        <ul class="nav nav-pills">
            <li class="nav-item"><a href="/" class="nav-link active" aria-current="page">Home</a></li>
            <li class="nav-item"><a href="/welcome-to-crm" class="nav-link">Get Started</a></li>
            <li class="nav-item"><a href="/login" class="nav-link">Sign In</a></li>
        </ul>
    </header>


  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

  <div class="background">
    <div class="container col-xxl-8 px-4 py-5">
      <div class="row flex-lg-row-reverse align-items-center g-5 py-5">
        <div class="col-10 col-sm-8 col-lg-6">
            <img src="https://jetpackcrm.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/resell-crm-hero-1024x788.png" class="d-block mx-lg-auto img-fluid" alt="Bootstrap Themes" width="700" height="500" loading="lazy">
        </div>
      <div class="col-lg-6">
          <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold lh-1 mb-3">MVP CRM & Landing Page Tracking</h1>
          <p class="lead">This project sets out to create a CRM application. Please see the below video for instructions</p>
          <button onclick="window.open('https://share.vidyard.com/watch/zjm2VeKXL4CKkJ3tTpysYR?','_blank')" class="shortcode-link comp-link lightbox-video" data-lightbox-uuid="sZLW7HbuBytapHnaGNDRYP"> watch a video to see how it works</button></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="background more-info">
  <div class="container col-xxl-8 px-4 py-5 more-info-container">
    <div class="row flex-lg-row align-items-center g-5 py-5 more-info-box">
        <div class="col-lg-6">
            <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold lh-1 mb-3 more-info-header">Contact Management</h1>
            <p class="lead more-info-lead">Both user can be easily managed contacts. User can add and create a contact with contact name, email and other information.</p>

        </div>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="background more-info">
  <div class="container col-xxl-8 px-4 py-5 more-info-container">
    <div class="row flex-lg-row-reverse align-items-center g-5 py-5 more-info-box">
      <div class="col-10 col-sm-8 col-lg-6 more-info-container-column">
      <img src="https://mcgaw.io/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/image1.png" class="d-block mx-lg-auto img-fluid" alt="Bootstrap Themes" width="700" height="500" loading="lazy">
    </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6">
            <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold lh-1 mb-3 more-info-header">Identity Management</h1>
            <p class="lead more-info-lead">In identity management, anonomous visitor are are tracked are able to be linked to contact record if the lead gives their email. Users might use different browsers, move from a mobile device to a laptop, or periodically clear browsing data. Identity management system offers the ability to link anonomous movements across different platforms, giving a holistic view of the user journey..</p>
        </div>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>

  <% yield %>
  </body>
</html>
